{"pageid":12977,"pagename":"Desert heat","title":"Desert heat","displaytitle":"Desert heat","revid":14278512,"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"description","value":"Desert heat is a game mechanic occurring in the Kharidian Desert south of the Shantay Pass. Every 30-90 seconds (depending on armour worn) a player spends in the desert, they will drink 1 dose of water from a waterskin in their inventory. Without any water to drink, the player takes around 10 damage. Wearing armour will decrease the interval from 90 seconds (when wearing no armour items) down to a minimum 30 seconds with full armour."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"noexcerpt noprint nomobile rs-external-header-links\" style=\"display:none\"><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rs\" data-text=\"RuneScape\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on Desert heat.\" data-site=\"rs\">The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://runescape.wiki/w/Desert_heat\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"rsw:Desert heat\">rsw:Desert heat</a></span></div>\n<p><b>Desert heat</b> is a game mechanic occurring in the <a href=\"/w/Kharidian_Desert\" title=\"Kharidian Desert\">Kharidian Desert</a> south of the <a href=\"/w/Shantay_Pass\" title=\"Shantay Pass\">Shantay Pass</a>. Every 30-90 seconds (depending on armour worn) a player spends in the desert, they will drink 1 dose of water from a waterskin in their inventory. Without any water to drink, the player takes around 10 damage. Wearing <a href=\"/w/Armour\" title=\"Armour\">armour</a> will decrease the interval from 90 seconds (when wearing no armour items) down to a minimum 30 seconds with full armour.\n</p><p>Players are not affected by desert heat while they are within the boundaries of towns or while a dialogue box is open.\n</p><p>Desert heat can kill players. Players should always enter the desert prepared, particularly those with low <a href=\"/w/Hitpoints\" title=\"Hitpoints\">Hitpoints</a> or <a href=\"/w/Hardcore_ironman\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hardcore ironman\">hardcore ironmen</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en-GB\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Protective_clothes_and_gear\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Protective clothes and gear</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Items\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Items</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Clothing\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Clothing</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Changes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Changes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Protective_clothes_and_gear\">Protective clothes and gear</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Desert_heat?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Protective clothes and gear\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Desert_heat?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Protective clothes and gear\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Items\">Items</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Desert_heat?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Items\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Desert_heat?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Items\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Waterskin\" title=\"Waterskin\">Waterskins</a> - Waterskins allow a player to survive the desert's heat effect, and can hold up to 4 doses of water. Each time a player drinks, one dose of water is used up. They can be filled to their maximum of 4 doses at a <a href=\"/w/Water_source\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Water source\">water source</a> or with the <a href=\"/w/Humidify\" title=\"Humidify\">Humidify</a> <a href=\"/w/Lunar_spell\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lunar spell\">Lunar spell</a> or by using a <a href=\"/w/Knife\" title=\"Knife\">knife</a> or <a href=\"/w/Slash\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slash\">slash</a> weapon on a <a href=\"/w/Kharidian_cactus\" title=\"Kharidian cactus\">Kharidian cactus</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Choc-ice\" title=\"Choc-ice\">Choc-ice</a> - Players who go to Nardah can buy choc-ice from <a href=\"/w/Rokuh\" title=\"Rokuh\">Rokuh</a>. They heal 6 <a href=\"/w/Hitpoints\" title=\"Hitpoints\">hitpoints</a> in addition to counting as a drink of water.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Circlet_of_water\" title=\"Circlet of water\">Circlet of water</a> - Each charge of the circlet counts as a dose of water when the circlet is worn.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Clothing\">Clothing</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Desert_heat?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Clothing\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Desert_heat?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Clothing\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Certain clothes protect against the desert heat by extending the time needed between drinks of water. These include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Desert_amulet_4\" title=\"Desert amulet 4\">Desert amulet 4</a> - Provides 100% protection against desert heat when worn. Rewarded from completing the <a href=\"/w/Elite_Desert_Diary\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Elite Desert Diary\">Elite Desert Diary</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Desert_clothing\" title=\"Desert clothing\">Desert clothing</a> - This set can be purchased from <a href=\"/w/Shantay\" title=\"Shantay\">Shantay</a> at <a href=\"/w/Shantay_Pass\" title=\"Shantay Pass\">Shantay Pass</a>, or from Ali Morrisane in Al Kharid.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Desert_outfit\" title=\"Desert outfit\">Desert outfit</a> - These outfit sets can be purchased from <a href=\"/w/Ali_Morrisane\" title=\"Ali Morrisane\">Ali Morrisane</a> in <a href=\"/w/Al_Kharid\" title=\"Al Kharid\">Al Kharid</a> during, or after, the <a href=\"/w/Rogue_Trader\" title=\"Rogue Trader\">Rogue Trader</a> <a href=\"/w/Miniquest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Miniquest\">miniquest</a>. The outfit differs slightly for male and female players.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Menaphite_clothing\" title=\"Menaphite clothing\">Menaphite clothing</a> - These sets can be purchased from Ali Morrisane in Al Kharid during, or after, the Rogue Trader miniquest. They come in two colour schemes, purple and red, which have identical bonuses.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Prospector_kit\" title=\"Prospector kit\">Prospector kit</a> - This set can be purchased from <a href=\"/w/Prospector_Percy\" title=\"Prospector Percy\">Prospector Percy</a> in the <a href=\"/w/Motherlode_Mine\" title=\"Motherlode Mine\">Motherlode Mine</a> using <a href=\"/w/Golden_nugget\" title=\"Golden nugget\">golden nuggets</a> obtained randomly from cleaning <a href=\"/w/Pay-dirt\" title=\"Pay-dirt\">pay-dirt</a>.</li></ul>\n<p>Note that players do not have to wear an entire set for the additional delay effect to happen. Each piece individually contributes to the delay.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<caption>Additional time (in seconds) provided per item\n</caption>\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Item set\n</th>\n<th>Helm\n</th>\n<th>Top\n</th>\n<th>Legs\n</th>\n<th>Boots\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Desert_clothing\" title=\"Desert clothing\">Desert clothing</a>\n</td>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td>+12\n</td>\n<td>+12\n</td>\n<td>+6\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Prospector_kit\" title=\"Prospector kit\">Prospector kit</a>\n</td>\n<td>+4\n</td>\n<td>+12\n</td>\n<td>+12\n</td>\n<td>+6\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Desert_outfit\" title=\"Desert outfit\">Desert outfit</a>\n</td>\n<td>+0\n</td>\n<td>+12 top,<br />+6 coat\n</td>\n<td>+12 (both<br />types)\n</td>\n<td>N/A\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Menaphite_clothing\" title=\"Menaphite clothing\">Menaphite clothing</a>\n</td>\n<td>+12\n</td>\n<td>+0\n</td>\n<td>+0\n</td>\n<td>N/A\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<ul><li class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></li></ul>\n<p>The maximum time between drinks is 132 seconds. This can be achieved by wearing desert robes in combination with a Menaphite hat.\n</p><p>It is a common misconception that the <a href=\"/w/Robe_of_elidinis_(top)\" title=\"Robe of elidinis (top)\">Robes of Elidinis</a> and <a href=\"/w/Slave_robes\" title=\"Slave robes\">slave robes</a> provide protection from desert heat. However, they do not.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Changes\">Changes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Desert_heat?section=4&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Desert_heat?action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible sortable\" style=\"max-width:800px\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Date\n</th>\n<th class=\"unsortable\">Changes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td data-sort-value=\"5 March 2015\"><a href=\"/w/5_March\" title=\"5 March\">5&#160;March</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2015\" title=\"2015\">2015</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:Achievement_Diaries\" title=\"Update:Achievement Diaries\">update</a>&#160;|&#160;<a href=\"/w/Poll:Old_School_Achievement_Diary_Rewards_Poll\" title=\"Poll:Old School Achievement Diary Rewards Poll\">poll</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Desert heat can now be nullified by wearing the <a href=\"/w/Desert_amulet_4\" title=\"Desert amulet 4\">Desert amulet 4</a>.\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Area effects\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Area_effects\" title=\"Template:Area effects\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Area_effects\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:Area_effects?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a href=\"/w/Area_effects\" title=\"Area effects\">Area effects</a></span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group navbox-group-split\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title-hidden\" colspan=\"0\" style=\"display:none\"></td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-list\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Darkness\" title=\"Darkness\">Darkness</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Desert heat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Swamp_decay\" title=\"Swamp decay\">Swamp decay</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Chill\" title=\"Chill\">Chill</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Vine_(Draynor_Manor)\" title=\"Vine (Draynor Manor)\">Vine (Draynor Manor)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Volcanic_eruption\" title=\"Volcanic eruption\">Volcanic eruption</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Desert heat gear\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Desert_heat_gear\" title=\"Template:Desert heat gear\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Desert_heat_gear\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:Desert_heat_gear?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Heat-resistant gear</a></span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\"><a href=\"/w/Desert_outfit\" title=\"Desert outfit\">Desert outfit</a></td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Desert_top\" title=\"Desert top\"><img alt=\"Desert top.png\" src=\"/images/Desert_top.png?3043c\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"30\" height=\"25\" data-file-width=\"30\" data-file-height=\"25\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Desert_top\" title=\"Desert top\">Top</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Desert_top_(over