=\"/w/Menaphite_purple_kilt\" title=\"Menaphite purple kilt\">Kilt</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Red</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Menaphite_red_hat\" title=\"Menaphite red hat\"><img alt=\"Menaphite red hat.png\" src=\"/images/Menaphite_red_hat.png?f1097\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"27\" data-file-width=\"20\" data-file-height=\"27\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Menaphite_red_hat\" title=\"Menaphite red hat\">Hat</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Menaphite_red_top\" title=\"Menaphite red top\"><img alt=\"Menaphite red top.png\" src=\"/images/Menaphite_red_top.png?92ebd\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"30\" height=\"25\" data-file-width=\"30\" data-file-height=\"25\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Menaphite_red_top\" title=\"Menaphite red top\">Top</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Menaphite_red_robe\" title=\"Menaphite red robe\"><img alt=\"Menaphite red robe.png\" src=\"/images/Menaphite_red_robe.png?92ebd\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"28\" data-file-width=\"20\" data-file-height=\"28\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Menaphite_red_robe\" title=\"Menaphite red robe\">Robe</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Menaphite_red_kilt\" title=\"Menaphite red kilt\"><img alt=\"Menaphite red kilt.png\" src=\"/images/Menaphite_red_kilt.png?92ebd\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"27\" height=\"24\" data-file-width=\"27\" data-file-height=\"24\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Menaphite_red_kilt\" title=\"Menaphite red kilt\">Kilt</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Others</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Waterskin\" title=\"Waterskin\"><img alt=\"Waterskin.png\" src=\"/images/Waterskin.png?30cdf\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"19\" height=\"24\" data-file-width=\"19\" data-file-height=\"24\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Waterskin\" title=\"Waterskin\">Waterskin</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Choc-ice\" title=\"Choc-ice\"><img alt=\"Choc-ice.png\" src=\"/images/Choc-ice.png?bcc94\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"20\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"20\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Choc-ice\" title=\"Choc-ice\">Choc-ice</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Desert_amulet_4\" title=\"Desert amulet 4\"><img alt=\"Desert amulet 4.png\" src=\"/images/Desert_amulet_4.png?3043c\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"28\" data-file-width=\"20\" data-file-height=\"28\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Desert_amulet_4\" title=\"Desert amulet 4\">Desert amulet 4</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Related</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Kharidian_cactus\" title=\"Kharidian cactus\">Kharidian cactus</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐7bfb498f95‐tvfj6\nCached time: 20220511103633\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.080 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.115 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 503/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 21346/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1243/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.011/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 924271/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   45.939      1 -total\n 39.25%   18.030      3 Template:Navbox\n 32.15%   14.771      1 Template:Area_effects\n 29.18%   13.405      1 Template:External\n 21.49%    9.873      1 Template:Desert_heat_gear\n 11.86%    5.449      1 Template:Ctg\n  8.85%    4.067      1 Template:Subject_changes\n  6.95%    3.191     18 Template:Plink\n  3.69%    1.697      1 Template:Subject_changes_header\n  3.40%    1.561      1 Template:Subject_changes_footer\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:12977-0!canonical and timestamp 20220511103633 and revision id 14278512. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{external|rs}}\n'''Desert heat''' is a game mechanic occurring in the [[Kharidian Desert]] south of the [[Shantay Pass]]. Every 30-90 seconds (depending on armour worn) a player spends in the desert, they will drink 1 dose of water from a waterskin in their inventory. Without any water to drink, the player takes around 10 damage. Wearing [[armour]] will decrease the interval from 90 seconds (when wearing no armour items) down to a minimum 30 seconds with full armour.\n\nPlayers are not affected by desert heat while they are within the boundaries of towns or while a dialogue box is open.\n\nDesert heat can kill players. Players should always enter the desert prepared, particularly those with low [[Hitpoints]] or [[hardcore ironman|hardcore ironmen]].\n\n==Protective clothes and gear==\n===Items===\n*[[Waterskin]]s - Waterskins allow a player to survive the desert's heat effect, and can hold up to 4 doses of water. Each time a player drinks, one dose of water is used up. They can be filled to their maximum of 4 doses at a [[water source]] or with the [[Humidify]] [[Lunar spell]] or by using a [[knife]] or [[slash]] weapon on a [[Kharidian cactus]].\n*[[Choc-ice]] - Players who go to Nardah can buy choc-ice from [[Rokuh]]. They heal 6 [[hitpoints]] in addition to counting as a drink of water.\n*[[Circlet of water]] - Each charge of the circlet counts as a dose of water when the circlet is worn. \n\n===Clothing===\nCertain clothes protect against the desert heat by extending the time needed between drinks of water. These include:\n*[[Desert amulet 4]] - Provides 100% protection against desert heat when worn. Rewarded from completing the [[Elite Desert Diary]].\n*[[Desert clothing]] - This set can be purchased from [[Shantay]] at [[Shantay Pass]], or from Ali Morrisane in Al Kharid.\n*[[Desert outfit]] - These outfit sets can be purchased from [[Ali Morrisane]] in [[Al Kharid]] during, or after, the [[Rogue Trader]] [[miniquest]]. The outfit differs slightly for male and female players.\n*[[Menaphite clothing]] - These sets can be purchased from Ali Morrisane in Al Kharid during, or after, the Rogue Trader miniquest. They come in two colour schemes, purple and red, which have identical bonuses.\n*[[Prospector kit]] - This set can be purchased from [[Prospector Percy]] in the [[Motherlode Mine]] using [[golden nugget]]s obtained randomly from cleaning [[pay-dirt]].\n\nNote that players do not have to wear an entire set for the additional delay effect to happen. Each piece individually contributes to the delay.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|+Additional time (in seconds) provided per item\n|-\n! Item set\n! Helm\n! Top\n! Legs\n! Boots\n|-\n| [[Desert clothing]] \n| N/A\n| +12\n| +12\n| +6\n|-\n| [[Prospector kit]]\n| +4\n| +12\n| +12\n| +6\n|-\n| [[Desert outfit]]\n| +0\n| +12 top,<br>+6 coat\n| +12 (both<br>types)\n| N/A\n|-\n| [[Menaphite clothing]]\n| +12\n| +0\n| +0\n| N/A\n|-\n|}\n*\n\nThe maximum time between drinks is 132 seconds. This can be achieved by wearing desert robes in combination with a Menaphite hat.\n\nIt is a common misconception that the [[Robe of elidinis (top)|Robes of Elidinis]] and [[slave robes]] provide protection from desert heat. However, they do not.\n\n==Changes==\n{{Subject changes header}}\n{{Subject changes\n|date = 5 March 2015\n|update = Achievement Diaries\n|poll = Old School Achievement Diary Rewards Poll\n|change = Desert heat can now be nullified by wearing the [[Desert amulet 4]].\n}}\n{{Subject changes footer}}\n\n{{Area effects}}\n{{Desert heat gear}}\n[[Category:Kharidian Desert]]\n[[Category:Mechanics]]"}